        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Public School Emergency Relief Act</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes a Department of Education program to provide temporary emergency impact aid payments to states for assisting local educational agencies and Indian schools in responding to increases in the enrollment of immigrant children. </p>]]></text>
